scene.message:
Maki: It really does seem like{nl}
we're the only ones with this{nl}
kind of power.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: I can't imagine Kandori{nl}
will stay quiet like this.{nl}
What will he pull next...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: That girl seems to{nl}
hold considerable power...{waitkey}If someone were misusing it,{nl}
that would be a problem.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: No matter what Demons{nl}
show up, we'll be fine!{waitkey}{clearbox}We just have to handle it{nl}
ourselves.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Even if someone looks{nl}
as sweet as an angel, that{nl}
doesn't mean the inside{nl}
matches.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Everywhere we go, it's{nl}
demons, demons~{waitkey}Isn't there anything more{nl}
fun to talk about?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: A kid who's too{nl}
naughty gets a spanking from{nl}
big brother here!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: There's something off{nl}
about this school. It's got{nl}
a weirdly fake smell to it.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: This really is{nl}
different from our school.{waitkey}No wonder it feels so fake{nl}
to me!{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: Lucky fools. Lazing{nl}
about without even knowing{nl}
what's happening.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Why is the girl in{nl}
black after this school? Has{nl}
she got some grudge or{nl}
something?{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Nothing could shock{nl}
me anymore!{waitkey}Like, even if I heard that{nl}
you could actually command{nl}
demons too!{waitkey}...Huh?{wait_fr:32} You really can?{wait_fr:48}{nl}
...Oh, come off it~! No way{nl}
that's true, right~?{waitkey}{ret}

Student: I just remembered — I{nl}
once met a girl in white.{waitkey}A girl dressed in white...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
but that's got nothing to do{nl}
with it, right?{waitkey}{ret}
